title: (Weds Full) Bobby’s Mount Rushmore of Tim McGraw Songs + Our Favorite Game: Was Amy Being Scammed? + How Much Did We Win the Lottery?  + Loser of the Draft
itunes:title: (Weds Full) Bobby’s Mount Rushmore of Tim McGraw Songs + Our Favorite Game: Was Amy Being Scammed? + How Much Did We Win the Lottery?  + Loser of the Draft
description:
Bobby was surprised just how many No. 1 songs Tim McGraw has had in his career. He decided to list his Mount Rushmore of Tim McGraw songs. Amy shares the latest scam that almost got her online…so just a warning NOT to do this. Lunchbox reveals how much we won in the lottery last night after we all went in on Lotto tickets. We also reveal the loser of the Country Superstars  Who Live the Most Normal Lives draft.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
